{"tid":272450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（RIP)前紐卡素中場迪奧迪赴中超掘金練波猝死終年30歲","createTime":"2017-06-05T23:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T05:42:34.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c492bf710310dc6311ccefd07c71c8808503dda","tid":272450,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:28:52.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d6676d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】今年2月才加盟中甲北京控股的前紐卡素中場迪奧迪，周一在操練期間突然昏厥，送院搶救後證實不治，<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/072848_2f605d91f8d8f245ffc80a1be8c966f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F072848_2f605d91f8d8f245ffc80a1be8c966f4.jpg&h=16f9917d&s={SIZE}\" />享年30歲。<br />\n<br />\n中甲球會北京控股周一晚發出官方聲明，確認曾效力紐卡素和川迪等歐洲球會的科特迪瓦中場迪奧迪（Cheick Tiote），在同日傍晚操練中突然昏迷，送院後證實不治：「2017年6月5日下午18時許，球隊開展正常訓練期間，科特迪瓦籍外援（迪奧迪）突發昏厥，俱樂部第一時間送往醫院搶救，終因搶救無效，於2017年6月5日19時許不幸辭世。目前俱樂部已與其家屬取得聯繫。」<br />\n<br />\n北京控股在聲明中續指：「（迪奧迪）先生於2017年2月5日加盟北京控股足球俱樂部，加盟以來（迪奧迪）先生為俱樂部做出了突出貢獻，並以其高超球技和職業精神獲得俱樂部、教練組和隊友們的高度評價。在此，北京控股足球俱樂部對（迪奧迪）先生的不幸辭世表示沉痛哀悼。」<br />\n<br />\n以30歲之齡與世長辭的迪奧迪，曾贏得比甲及荷甲冠軍，科特迪瓦2015年成為非國盃盟主，他亦是冠軍成員之一。多名曾與迪奧迪共事的現役或退役球員，都透過社交媒體哀悼這位昔日戰友，其中效力曼城的比利時國腳高柏尼在Twitter留言道：「我無言，而且非常傷感。迪奧迪是我擁有過最友善和最硬淨的隊友之一。安息吧，兄弟。」"},{"pid":"a4d1e7f7d2d0a9812fcf26ebdc1d004b1a983e80","tid":272450,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0779276d176bf845e1704837b1187447ebb42789","tid":272450,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:34:43.000Z","msg":"毒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de582a4ac277627a70be78d2e1f3be669a7b902","tid":272450,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有害氣體無害"},{"pid":"328000d86779728fe8255f929d54d728943d4d46","tid":272450,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:00:23.000Z","msg":"免費吊女，出得太多"},{"pid":"c4c77ac87887b0563a9346425a66d0fae7b2abbb","tid":272450,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>免費吊女，出得太多</blockquote><br />\n咪傻<br />\n你估佢係外國冇屌過女咩<br />\n擺明就支那空氣差啦"},{"pid":"8fad41e4a51c214c921ad8d3cc808fd50bf38559","tid":272450,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:32:28.000Z","msg":"北京仲難踢過俄仔個零下幾度主場&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"f2eab9b744d630d24d88be45f47a4bccc9583843","tid":272450,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:33:16.000Z","msg":"霧霾引致心臟病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d9fdca7ae8b089f45a2e93be96fc1f222bebfc","tid":272450,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:50:38.000Z","msg":"毒霧害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c762e2bdc556851809c1f1385127b74f55dd3f","tid":272450,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}